text:
@AabhasVerma5 See, dubbing in a regional language is a must so that people who aren‚Äôt well versed in english can enjoy.
But people who can read and speak english should definitely go for the original w/ english subtitles.

name: Bhuvan Bam
text:
For example:

Thai: Swadika...
English dubbing: Hello..
UTV Movies dubbing: Aaja bidhu tera intezaar tha..

name: Bhuvan Bam
text:
Dear movie lovers,
If you have started watching foreign cinema, please try watching it in the original language only. Reading subtitles is difficult in the beginning but once you get hold of it, the fun multiplies. English dubbed world cinema often loses its essence. Your views?
